data.description: Coveted North facing corner unit with extra large patio space. Grill and water access just steps from your living room. Scored concrete floors w/ cool modern finishes include custom cabinets, new Jenn Air appliances, and Carrera marble bathrooms. Master bedroom has additional private balcony. 2 reserved parking spaces just below condo in parking deck. Building amenities include pool, concierge, urban garden, tennis and basketball courts, fitness center, dog walk and 20th floor River Room.
